{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Integrate-OUDS","text":"Integrate OUDS"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Use-Swift-Package-Manager","text":"Use Swift Package Manager"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to add the iOS library of "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Unified Design System"}]},{"type":"text","text":", you need to add our "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}]},{"type":"text","text":" into your project."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To do that, add a new "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"package dependency"}]},{"type":"text","text":" to your "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode"}]},{"type":"text","text":" project by refering to it by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You are free to choose wether or not you want a branch or a specific tag, pick the solution you want."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki\/50-%E2%80%90-About-versions,-releases-and-builds"},{"type":"text","text":" for more details about versions, releases and tags. You can find release tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.18.0"}]},{"type":"text","text":") and release candidates tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.18.0-rc3"}]},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Import-the-librairies-you-need","text":"Import the librairies you need"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You should use one (or several) of the following imports for your needs, which are basically "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}]},{"type":"text","text":" products."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We recommend to embed in your apps only the ones you need to avoid to embed useless assets."}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Tip","style":"tip"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["import OUDSThemesContract \/\/ If you want to define your theme, use themes or OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSModules \/\/ To use modules","import OUDSComponents \/\/ To use components","import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To use the default Orange theme","import OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools \/\/ To use the Orange Business Tools theme","import OUDSThemesSosh \/\/ To use the Sosh theme","import OUDSThemesWireframe \/\/ To use the Wireframe theme","import OUDSTokensComponent \/\/ If you need to override or use directly components tokens","import OUDSTokenSemantic \/\/ If you need to override or use directly semantic tokens","import OUDSTokensRaw \/\/ If you need to override or use directly raw tokens","import OUDSFoundations \/\/ For some utilities"],"syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Or-more-simple-import-umbrella-library","text":"Or more simple, import umbrella library"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We do not recommend this solution because from our point of view use of tailored imports is better to import only the needed elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use of umbrella products can increase app sizes and needed storage because it emebds plenty of assets (images, fonts, etc.)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and useless constants."}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Note","style":"note"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Import the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}]},{"type":"text","text":" product which suits your needs:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"table","header":"row","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Umbrella"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUI"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above and all themes"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrange"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Orange Business Tools themes"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIWireframe"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Wireframe theme"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrangeSosh"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Sosh themes"}]}]]]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Chose-your-theme","text":"Chose your theme"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Unified Design System"}]},{"type":"text","text":" framework provides today four themes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"table","header":"row","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Theme"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default one for Orange products and can be enriched \/ derivated"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Business Tools"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For some Orange products with heavy \/ rich UI and dimensions constraints"}]}]],[[{"ty